{"tid":2122301,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓貓絕育問題","createTime":"2020-07-24T02:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T11:05:39.000Z","uid":36195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e255649905be59763b49af4ab6fea29a2451dc8","tid":2122301,"uid":36195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:24:36.000Z","msg":"又係新手貓奴問問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兩隻主子話咁快就打哂三針要開始諗絕育問題<br />\n因為佢哋係一仔一女所以我都比較擔心<br />\n想問下大家嘅貓仔貓女係幾多個月大絕育<br />\n我見有幾派嘅說法 <br />\n我睇皇阿瑪佢哋就話女仔早啲絕育好啲<br />\n貓仔有啲人又話可以早啲絕<br />\n有啲人話太早絕育個頭會細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以想問下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50eb81439a3e79de57c66f3f650824bbee708159","tid":2122301,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:26:43.000Z","msg":"你生活係咪多2部流動CCTV~"},{"pid":"0df919f4c59c40ee1299ea4c3fd87e91eff8ba35","tid":2122301,"uid":299102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T04:41:12.000Z","msg":"我有一隻仔 上網刨post啲人都話仔1歳絕等佢尿道個啲發育會好啲 不過如果佢之後會賴尿個啲就要即刻帶佢會絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 貓女就唔肯定 你打針有冇問過醫生意見？"},{"pid":"1f7567c084411081c4b58ed70aa6961ff37bfa10","tid":2122301,"uid":346480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:58:45.000Z","msg":"貓女可以好早發情，到時要隔開佢哋，等貓女發情期完左就應該可以去絕育<br />\n我屋企只係有貓仔，所以會等佢8個月以上先絕，但如果佢亂咁屙尿的話咁你就一定要快啲拎埋隻貓仔去絕育了"},{"pid":"12f3960b6bc50a01c2a60b42209a835e94d4363a","tid":2122301,"uid":36195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"下星期先打最後一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時會再問吓醫生意見<br />\n我見啲人話貓女最好發情前絕育<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602ba5628ba24b88c437d219f2798c337201343c","tid":2122301,"uid":261522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"貓女六個月可以，"},{"pid":"78f483b6f9b3de6dcb9e268932a2083e5d8b6794","tid":2122301,"uid":364011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"我都係一仔一女領養, 大慨6-8個月就絕育"}]}